title: Case Logic QNS-113 13.3-Inch EVA Molded Laptop / Macbook Air / Pro Retina Display Sleeve (Black)
description: Designed for the digital gypsy who needs only a laptop to keep in touch and informed, this sleek, molded attaché features eye-catching style and great protection for laptops up to 13.3-Inch. The elegant tone-on-tone linear accents were inspired by the familiar texture of seat belts. For a desk-on-the-go, the clamshell design and integrated airflow channels allow in-case use and minimize the risk of overheating. Features: Thick, quilted padding keeps your laptop protected and snugly in place to prevent it from sliding around; Interior stabilizing band ensures your laptop stays put when opening or closing the case; Padded handles provide comfortable transportation; 25 year warranty. Fits 12 to 13.3-Inch netbooks and laptops; External Dimensions 14.2 x 11 x 1.8-Inch; Laptop Compartment 13 x 9.4 x 1.5-Inch
